attributes.action: Offer COVID-19 boosters to all over 50s, asthmatics and long Covid sufferers
attributes.additional_details: We believe the COVID-19 autumn programme unfairly excludes certain people, and that widening entitlement would better protect the public and create financial savings.
attributes.background: We want the Government to offer the autumn Covid-19 booster vaccinations to all over 50s, asthmatics and long Covid sufferers.
